name: Handmade Uganda Paper Beads #14
description:
These are fair-trade, and eco-friendly. Each paper bead is handmade by women in Uganda from old magazines, catalogs and calendars. 

Your purchase will help to build a school in South Sudan's Upper Nile State, to serve repatriated refugees from the Second Sudan Civil War. Many refugees have lived in refugee camps outside of their homeland continuously since 1985. Our ministry will provide a school, church and micro enterprises to support newly repatriated refugees.
